Privacy Policy
Personal Information
“AppBook” doesn’t collect any personal information and doesn’t share it with third parties. Period. The only place where your data might be stored is your own device.
Internet Access
“AppBook” doesn't contain any links. All links opened in AppBook are relevant to the content that's being consumed, which is loaded entirely from iTunes API. Nothing is generated or tweaked by us.
“AppBook” is partly functional offline. Internet connection is required to load latest content from Apple servers through iTunes API directly. All communications are depersonalized and it’s impossible to get any personally identifiable information from them.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about your privacy feel free to contact us at
appbook.appstore@gmail.com